Wifi Tether for Root Users - Android - Open Garden
* Open Garden Release 2.0.7.1 (Chihuahua)
* 03/08/2011 - 2.0.7 base update, extended user interface
* 02/20/2011 - 2.0.6 + updated Internationalization
* 01/27/2011 - 2.0.5 http://opengarden.com/og.wifi-tether/source
* 12/21/2010 - 2.0.1 Wireless interface set up in AdHoc-Mode. 
--------------------------------------------------------------
Proof-of-Technology - OG Mesh Protocol. 
Open Garden Wifi Tether shares the handset network connection (GPRS/EDGE/UMTS/HSDPA), creating an ad-hoc Wifi Access HotSpot.
--------------------------------------------------------------
This program enables ad-hoc tethering (wifi and bluetooth).
*** Requirements:
*** This application requires root-permission ***
*** on the device
